              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Each Si-foil piece was mounted on a Ti-foil (purity",
                "99.6%, thickness 20 mum, diameter 13 mm) by",
                "fixing it with glue at two peripheral points of the",
